videos.headline: Arkansas wins at the horn in incredible shot-making sequence
videos.description: Vanderbilt's Marnelle Garraud sinks a deep 3 to tie the score, then Arkansas' Makayla Daniels answers with an even deeper trey to win it for the Razorbacks.
